      "body": ":+1:\r\n\r\nAlso, lowercase float and double literals: `1f` and `1d` instead of `1F` and `1D`. The latter tends to more easily be interpreted as hexadecimal, for some weird cognitive reason.\r\n\r\nPS: you can enable that by default to the `--Scala.js` style as well."
    }
