  "created_at": "2016-05-28 15:51:33 UTC",
  "updated_at": "2016-05-28 16:17:02 UTC",
  "closed_at": null,
  "body": "Taken from Spark coding style: https://github.com/databricks/scala-style-guide/blob/master/README.md#long-literals\r\n\r\nOriginal:\r\n```scala\r\n11l\r\n```\r\n\r\nScalafmt:\r\n```scala\r\n11l\r\n```\r\n\r\nI would like the input to look like this:\r\n```scala\r\n11L\r\n```\r\n\r\nUsing:\r\n* 0.2.5\r\n* --style default\r\n"
}